# WhatsApp-automatic-message

1. Download python for your system using link given in repo.
2. Download chromedriver given in the repo.
3. If the chromedriver does not match your system, please download using link given in repo.
4. Download the OpenWhatsApp.png file in repo if you have WhatsApp installed on your PC and want to use receiver's WhatsApp number for messaging.
5. If you have WhatsApp PC installed , then you need to run the first program in repo on python.
6. If you want to use WhatsApp web, then run the second program in the repo on python.
7. You will be asked the path/address of the OpenWhatsApp.png image and chromedriver on your PC, so make sure you download them to a known location.
